{"tid":407713,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人對日本神話有興趣?","createTime":"2017-09-20T15:42:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-10T19:18:08.000Z","uid":5818,"like":81,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":56,"replies":[{"pid":"c418290ea478b392a383c0ad427b7fd247cefcd5","tid":407713,"uid":5818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T15:42:53.000Z","msg":"大家好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  其實小弟一直都對日本神話非常之感興趣，咁啱又睇到啲資料係講日本神話，所以想係到同大家分享下，討論下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">其實係想練下日文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span><br />\n小弟可能寫得1999，還請多多指教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>序\t日本神話時代與記紀神話</ins></strong><br />\n日本嘅神祗多不勝數：伊邪那岐、伊邪那美、天照、<span style=\"font-size: small;\">無限</span>月讀、須佐之男等等，相信大家都喺game呀動畫中聽過下咁，但當中眾神嘅來源係咩呢？佢地之間又有咩故事呢？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n記紀神話係指<span style=\"color: red;\">《古事記》</span>同<span style=\"color: blue;\">《日本書紀》</span>兩本書中記載嘅神代史，同時亦都係日本神話嘅經典作之一。兩本書名雖然唔同，但亦都有記載住相似嘅神話故事同歷史事件，所以我地就叫佢地所記載嘅神話同歷史做<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">記紀神話</span>啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://www3.pref.nara.jp/miryoku/narakikimanyo/images/chigai/chigai_img01.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww3.pref.nara.jp%2Fmiryoku%2Fnarakikimanyo%2Fimages%2Fchigai%2Fchigai_img01.jpg&h=f37a94f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《古事記》為現今發現日本最早嘅歷史書，由日本嘅神話時代開始記載，直至因聖德太子攝政而變得出名嘅推古天皇之間嘅事蹟。《古事記》分為上中下三卷，其中<span style=\"color: red;\">只係得上卷（旧辞）有收錄唔同嘅日本神話同埋傳說</span>，而中下卷（帝紀）就紀錄天皇家嘅家譜以及佢地嘅事跡。所以話，《古事記》係集日本各地口耳相傳落嚟嘅神話同歷史所編纂嘅一本經典史書。<br />\n而《日本書紀》其實係為了海外(因為成本書都係以漢字記錄)而撰寫嘅日本正史，由日本第一位天皇&mdash;天武天皇嘅仔舍人親王所寫。但<span style=\"color: blue;\">《日本書紀》全書三十卷中就只有卷一同卷二（神代）詳細記錄住日本神話</span>。<br />\n小弟將會參考記紀神話同埋唔同嘅資料，同大家分享下日本神明佢地嘅故事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n小弟主要嘅參考資料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :<br />\n<a href=\"http://nihonsinwa.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnihonsinwa.com%2F&d=Saleply5TRv7NA95VFOxyZ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=4fc8dc18\" target=\"_blank\">http://nihonsinwa.com/</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://kojiki.co/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fkojiki.co%2F&d=Saleply5TRv7NA95VFOxyZ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=0c5aa533\" target=\"_blank\">http://kojiki.co/</a>"},{"pid":"e978dcab40dcddb52a5284eab9d31d0e60bbdecf","tid":407713,"uid":33380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T15:45:15.000Z","msg":"有興趣"},{"pid":"a17cfae2de20394dba32f1ed345c9311c3235e97","tid":407713,"uid":5818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T15:56:09.000Z","msg":"<strong><ins>第一章\t天地開闢及造化三神</ins></strong><br />\n現時嘅日本可以分成三個領域：「眾神居住嘅天界」，「人類居住嘅世間」以及「死者居住嘅冥界」(天界即係俗稱嘅高天原)<br />\n<br />\n但係喺天地仲未形成嘅時候，世界仲係處於一個混沌嘅狀態。直至混沌開始分開啦，一啲澄明而較輕嘅物質就會形成天；相反混濁而較重嘅物質就會形成地。一開始係天先形成，之後先到地下，經過好耐時間，天地就形成了。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://nihonsinwa.com/photo/80IucN.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnihonsinwa.com%2Fphoto%2F80IucN.jpeg&h=ff5bbc5a&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n天地分開，神就誕生了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n神話史上第一位神明&mdash;<span style=\"color: red;\">天御中主神</span>（アメノミナカヌシノカミ）喺天地初開後誕生。同佢個名一樣啦，天御中主神被視為「天界嘅中心領袖」，亦都因為佢係第一位日本神明，所以被視為最偉大嘅神明。天御中主神其實冇乜技能可言，而且一直都匿埋喺天界乜都唔做，但就被視為係眾神首領嘅象徵，其實乜都冇做過 <span style=\"font-size: small;\">(別名天界freerider / 廢老)</span>。<br />\n<br />\n其後，第二位神明誕生了&mdash;<span style=\"color: blue;\">高御產巢日神</span>（タカミムスビノカミ）。因為高御産巢日神生得同棵樹一樣高大，所以又稱「高木神」(其實只係個名字too long didnt read而幫佢改一個短啲嘅別名，好似係)。其後因為天界除咗freerider之外亦都冇其他神明所以覺得太悶，所以衪就學天御中主神一樣freeride了一陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n佢個名「たかみむすびのかみ」，其中「高御(たかみ)」係高木神(たかぎのかみ) 嘅簡稱；「産巢(むす)」代表生產，生命嘅誕生；而「日(び)」就代表太陽。將「高大嘅樹木」、「生產」同埋「太陽」嘅意思結合，就有「孕育生命」嘅意思了。(另一方面「産巢日(むすび)」音同「結び(むすび)」，有扑野嘅意思)<br />\n<img src=\"http://nihonsinwa.com/photo/s9HlMl.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnihonsinwa.com%2Fphoto%2Fs9HlMl.jpeg&h=a5a7784a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n老實講比起天御中主神，高御産巢日神更加似眾神之首，在天上守護住日本。但因為衪嘅存在感實在低到who fucking cares <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，所以眾神大抵都認為天御中主神先係眾神之首。<br />\n<br />\n喺高御産巢日神誕下不久，第三位神明亦誕生了&mdash;<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">神產巢日神</span>（カムムスビノカミ）。<br />\n高御產巢日神同神產巢日神一般都被視為<strong>父性同母性，陰陽兩儀嘅象徵</strong>，但其實三位神明都冇所謂「性別」的概念，所以現今會以「<strong>獨神</strong>(ひとりがみ)」，即係冇女屌又冇仔生，嚟稱呼佢地。(但事實上因為神產巢日神嘅形象同女性相若，所以一般都會認為佢係代表母性嘅一方嘅)<br />\n<br />\n就係咁，三位最重要嘅神明誕生了，後人將依三位<del>freerider</del>神明冠以「造化三神」之稱啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n下一章將會同大家一齊睇下五柱別天津神同埋神世七代<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e027b5864cf2ff8c4dabd60218fdd61a70b59ea","tid":407713,"uid":11261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T15:58:39.000Z","msg":"Lm<br />\n之前都日本買書睇過"},{"pid":"8b5e12190da231fadc7209dae41c5c204d9e1fee","tid":407713,"uid":47356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T15:59:36.000Z","msg":"liked"},{"pid":"708bfd7b33c6507eb909e9334e78c5650447ffca","tid":407713,"uid":57407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T16:00:21.000Z","msg":"LM之後再睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"860695aad9ab3efee079f72b7b2513f4f6f6ef2d","tid":407713,"uid":52793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T16:01:09.000Z","msg":"FYP做神話，巴打交流吓"},{"pid":"6f2df5ff90934ffe38b198c06c5c818516c8d20c","tid":407713,"uid":5818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T16:04:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>FYP做神話，巴打交流吓</blockquote><br />\n巴打都係做日本神話?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  賜教賜教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45e5282f486ae2889d236f81667f363ede15e9fe","tid":407713,"uid":54733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T16:19:41.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"0454ae288d962ea516521e5e6cf7a2f3b10700f6","tid":407713,"uid":136727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T16:23:01.000Z","msg":"樓主對別天神有乜睇法?<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7834cfee63261e17e42c588fa67a61534140ea9c","tid":407713,"uid":146807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T16:23:44.000Z","msg":"原本一直以為天照係最大粒嘅日本神 原來唔係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nLm學嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53edfee8442a635d180e2f86ce17c5be2f1a272b","tid":407713,"uid":122211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T16:26:40.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"3f0d3ef0275aeb46407d1b76f98d9e81e75e0797","tid":407713,"uid":145220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T16:26:43.000Z","msg":"留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3fd1e5b16bf008a5537de0e1bde7d7e312d525c","tid":407713,"uid":5818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T16:28:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主對別天神有乜睇法?<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n止水好型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"449eb3db36168bbb60821be70b7ecfd7c21a5ca4","tid":407713,"uid":54282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T16:34:47.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"e7b0016879ac16417a0808b0a8348b400d3c3628","tid":407713,"uid":136727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T16:36:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>樓主對別天神有乜睇法?<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n止水好型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁依邪那歧同依邪那美兩兄妹點睇?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d95aaaaecf79eb913ff6a31a2f811fc5ceb8f04","tid":407713,"uid":57228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T16:49:24.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"acd174a72e9f16693e82b649c4e85f59239368db","tid":407713,"uid":83446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T16:50:30.000Z","msg":"每次睇到 迦具土 出世就想笑"},{"pid":"84167216d535d5cbe1731360011fee058a9f2777","tid":407713,"uid":10652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T16:51:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dca978e2712b2ddcae1e3e276c119723a531c41d","tid":407713,"uid":146583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T16:51:52.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"4a4b390cea02d7476bac6b5154364944593ba7b0","tid":407713,"uid":10652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T16:52:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>每次睇到 迦具土 出世就想笑</blockquote><br />\n燒你個臭閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50d